			        <div class="panel">
			            <div  class="question">
			            	How many bookings is a pet sitter allowed to handle within same period ?
			                <img  class="arrow down" src="assets/arrow-down.svg">
			                <img  class="arrow up collapse" src="assets/arrow-up.svg">
			            </div>
			            <div  class="answer collapse">
