        		<td>

        			<h3> Payments </h3>

        			<div class="panel">
			            <div  class="question">
			            	Does PetCare handle online payments of a pet stay/booking ?
			                <img  class="arrow down" src="assets/arrow-down.svg">
			                <img  class="arrow up collapse" src="assets/arrow-up.svg">
			            </div>
			            <div  class="answer collapse">
			            	As of now PetCare DOES NOT handle any form of online payment, however , the PetCare is working towards integrating this component in the coming future. Payments of the bookings are made on a personal level between pet sitter and pet owner on either the drop off date or pick up date preferrably the pick up date.    
			                 
			            </div>
        			</div>
        			<br>
			        <div class="panel">
			            <div  class="question">
			            	Can a different payment be agreed upon by a pet owner and pet sitter ?
			                <img  class="arrow down" src="assets/arrow-down.svg">
			                <img  class="arrow up collapse" src="assets/arrow-up.svg">
			            </div>
			            <div  class="answer collapse">
			              Yes, a pet owner and pet sitter can decide upon a different price but both parties must agree otherwise we default back to the price as displayed by the system.
			            </div>
			        </div>




